sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Dev as Developer
    participant SK as Spec Kit
    participant CA as Code Assistant
    participant LLM as LLM
    box rgba(120, 170, 200, 0.10) MCP servers
    participant CON as Confluence
    participant JIRA as Jira
    end
    box rgba(200, 160, 80, 0.10) Corporate-standard skills
    participant MK as Maker skills
    participant CK as Checker skills
    end

    Dev->>CA: build the feature
    CA->>CON: fetch feature spec (via MCP)
    CON-->>CA: feature description

    rect rgba(130, 110, 200, 0.06)
    Note over Dev,CK: 1 - Constitution (encode your standards)
    CA->>MK: apply standards
    MK-->>CA: principles and guardrails
    loop reason and draft
        CA->>LLM: draft constitution
        LLM-->>CA: draft
    end
    CA->>SK: /constitution
    SK-->>CA: constitution.md
    end

    rect rgba(130, 110, 200, 0.06)
    Note over Dev,CK: 2 - Specify, plan and tasks (you steer)
    CA->>MK: apply standards
    MK-->>CA: drafting guidance
    loop reason and draft
        CA->>LLM: draft spec
        LLM-->>CA: draft
    end
    CA->>SK: /specify
    SK-->>CA: spec.md
    CA->>CK: review spec
    CK-->>CA: pass or issues
    CA->>Dev: /clarify questions
    Dev-->>CA: answers and edits
    CA->>SK: /plan
    SK-->>CA: plan.md
    CA->>SK: /tasks
    SK-->>CA: tasks.md
    CA->>JIRA: create tickets from tasks
    JIRA-->>CA: ticket IDs
    CA->>Dev: review the drafts
    Dev-->>CA: approve to build
    end

    rect rgba(130, 110, 200, 0.06)
    Note over Dev,CK: 3 - Implement
    CA->>JIRA: pull next ticket
    JIRA-->>CA: ticket details
    CA->>MK: apply standards
    MK-->>CA: coding guidance
    loop agentic loop - generate, write files, run tests
        CA->>LLM: generate code
        LLM-->>CA: code and next action
    end
    CA->>SK: /implement
    SK-->>CA: code + tests
    CA->>CK: review code
    CK-->>CA: pass or fix
    end

    CA-->>Dev: ready for review
    Dev->>JIRA: close ticket (human gate)
    Note over Dev,JIRA: loop back - iterate on feedback
